sney%20costume%20I%20was%20pissed%20(drunk)%20quite%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20time%20because%20there%20was%20no%20other%20way%20to%20get%20your%20head%20around%20what%20was%20going%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20it%20was%20fun%20but%20parts%20of%20being%20famous%20and%20being%20on%20tour%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.menshealth.com.au%2Fliam-payne-july-2019-mens-health-cover%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bjust%20got%20a%20little%20bit%20toxic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThat%20same%20year%2C%20Payne%20said%20he'd%20like%20to%20collaborate%20with%20Styles.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22475%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22one%20direction%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5dd6bb6479d7570a8942dda4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22357%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELiam%20Payne%20and%20Harry%20Styles%20have%20different%20music%20styles.%3Cp%3EEthan%20Miller%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20iHeartMedia%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20November%202019%20interview%20with%20the%20%26quot%3BHits%20Radio%20Breakfast%20Show%2C%26quot%3B%20Payne%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplanetradio.co.uk%2Fhits-radio%2Fentertainment%2Fcelebrity%2Fliam-payne-harry-styles-collaboration%2F%5C%22%3Ehe'd%20be%20interested%20in%20collaborating%20with%20Styles%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20even%20though%20he%20once%20said%20he%20wasn't%20a%20huge%20fan%20of%20his%20music.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20the%20first%20song%20off%20his%20album%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20me%20and%20Harry%20could%20do%20a%20really%20cool%20song%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20the%20show%2C%20speaking%20of%20Styles'%20album%20%26quot%3BFine%20Line%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20first%20single%20from%20it%2C%20%26quot%3BLights%20Up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20could%20be%20a%20good%20mix%20between%20the%20two%20things%20because%20the%20first%20song%20was%20kind%20of%20funky%20so%20I%20feel%20like%20we%20coul