th%2C%20a%20PM%20at%20Parnassus%20Investments.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EKeith%20shares%204%20mid-cap%20stocks%20dominating%20their%20industries%20and%20on%20track%20to%20be%20tomorrow's%20mega-caps.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20invested%20%241%2C000%20in%20Nvidia%20just%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20you'd%20have%20over%20%2427%2C500%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20to%20maximizing%20stock-market%20returns%20is%20to%20buy%20in%20early%20before%20the%20hype.%20The%20Magnificent%20Seven%20have%20incredibly%20high%20market%20caps%20now%2C%20but%20they%20were%20small-%20and%20mid-sized%20companies%20before%20they%20were%20market%20behemoths.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20why%20Lori%20Keith%2C%20director%20of%20research%20and%20portfolio%20manager%20at%20Parnassus%20Investments%2C%20is%20such%20a%20big%20fan%20of%20mid-cap%20stocks.%20Keith%20oversees%20%243.2%20billion%20of%20assets%20in%20the%20Parnassus%20Mid%20Cap%20Fund.%20Her%20investment%20strategy%20centers%20on%20finding%20quality%20companies%20with%20long%20runways%20for%20revenue%20and%20profit%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestor%20sentiment%20this%20year%20has%20been%20mainly%20focused%20on%20mega-caps%20and%20small-caps%2C%20with%20not%20much%20appreciation%20for%20the%20middle.%20But%20Keith%20believes%20mid-caps%20offer%20the%20best%20of%20both%20worlds.%20Small%20caps%20have%20high%20growth%20potential%20but%20are%20also%20high-risk%20and%20often%20unprofitable.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20large%20caps%20may%20have%20difficulty%20sustaining%20high%20growth%20rates%20going%20forward%2C%20meaning%20that%20there's%20limited%20upside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMid-cap%20companies%20are%20usually%20defined%20as%20those%20with%20market%20caps%20from%20around%20%242%20billion%20to%20%2410%20billion%2C%20but%20Keith%20takes%20a%20more%20liberal%20definition%2C%20considering%20companies%20valued%20even%20over%20%24100%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20really%20attractive%20place%20for%20investors%2C%26quot%3B%20Keith%20said%20of%20mid-cap%20stocks.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20really%20strong%20defendable%20businesses%20that%20often%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20capture%20additional%20growth%20relative%20to%20the%20large-cap%20stocks%20that%20are%20a%20bit%20more%20saturated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mid-caps%20with%20the%20most%20potential%20are%20usually%20not%20household%20names%2C%20Keith%20said.%20But%20they%20do%20have%20strong%20balance%20sheets%20with%20plentiful%20free%20cash%20flow%20and%20low%20debt%2C%20and%20often%20have%20sufficient%20capital%20to%20expand%20overseas%20and%20fund%20acquisitions.%20And%20most%20importantly%2C%20Keith%20is%20looking%20for%20companies%20with%20a%20differentiated%20product%20in%20the%20market%2C%20or%20what%20Warren%20Buffett%20has%20dubbed%20an%20%26quot%3Beconomic%20moat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20this%20strategy%2C%20several%20of%20Keith's%20picks%20have%20quickly%20expanded%20their%20businesses%20and%20outgrown%20the%20mid-cap%20label.%20Keith%20is%20particularly%20bullish%20on%20mid-caps%20in%20areas%20of%20the%20market%20such%20as%20software%2C%20semiconductors%2C%20real%20estate%2C%20and%20healthcare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelow%2C%20she%20shares%204%20mid-cap%20companies%20with%20strong%20long-term%20growth%20prospects%20and%20the%20potential%20to%20become%20market%20dominants.%20They%20are%20all%20constituents%20of%20the%20Parnassus%20Mid%20Cap%20Fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ace093b0-e584-488a-aa96-febf2107aea0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E4%20mid-caps%20set%20to%20become%20the%20mega-caps%20of%20the%20future%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECBRE%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22792%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CBRE%20one%20year%20stock%20performance%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67102fb33f2165d716e25e94%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22656%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMarkets%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan