n%20a%20post%20on%20X%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Zeeshan%20Siddique%20wrote%3A%20%26quot%3BMy%20father%20lost%20his%20life%20protecting%20and%20saving%20the%20lives%20and%20homes%20of%20poor%20innocent%20people.%20Today%2C%20my%20family%20is%20broken%20but%20his%20death%20must%20not%20be%20politicised%20and%20definitely%20not%20go%20in%20vain.%20I%20NEED%20JUSTICE%2C%20MY%20FAMILY%20NEEDS%20JUSTICE!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBaba%20Siddique%2C%2066%2C%20was%20shot%20dead%20by%20three%20men%20outside%20Zeeshan's%20Bandra%20East%20office%20around%209.30%20pm%20on%20Dussehra%2C%20October%2013.%20Police%20had%20said%20six%20bullets%20were%20fired%20at%20him%2C%20four%20of%20which%20hit%20him%20and%20another%20hit%20an%20aide%20in%20the%20leg.%20Siddique%20was%20rushed%20to%20the%20Lilavati%20Hospital%2C%20where%20he%20was%20declared%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20of%20the%20shooters%2C%20Gurmail%20Baljit%20Singh%20from%20Haryana%20and%20Dharamraj%20Kashyap%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20were%20arrested%20soon%20after%20the%20murder%20while%20Shiv%20Kumar%20Gautam%2C%20who%20is%20also%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20is%20on%20the%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20Kashyap%20had%20claimed%20in%20a%20Mumbai%20court%20that%20his%20age%20was%2017%20despite%20his%20Aadhar%20card%20stating%20that%20he%20was%2019%2C%20and%20a%20bone%20ossification%20test%20had%20been%20ordered.%20On%20Monday%2C%20the%20results%20of%20the%20test%20proved%20that%20he%20is%20not%20a%20minor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20sources%20said%20the%20suspects%20have%20claimed%20that%20they%20work%20for%20gangster%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%2C%20who%20is%20lodged%20in%20Gujarat's%20Sabarmati%20jail%2C%20and%20the%20same%20claim%20was%20made%20in%20a%20social%20media%20post%20on%20Sunday.%20The%20Facebook%20post%20was%20made%20on%20the%20handle%20of%20one%20Shubuu%20Lonkar%2C%20believed%20to%20be%20Bishnoi%20gang%20associate%20Shubham%20Rameshwar%20Lonkar%2C%20claiming%20responsibility%20for%20the%20murder