n%20half-cook%20your%20chicken%20for%20about%2010%20minutes%20at%20400%20Fahrenheit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20want%20to%20get%20a%20nice%20char%20on%20the%20chicken%20in%20the%20oven%20when%20you're%20baking%20at%20home%20before%20mixing%20it%20with%20our%20sauce.%20At%20the%20restaurant%2C%20of%20course%2C%20we%20add%20it%20to%20the%20tandoor%2C%20which%20gives%20it%20a%20nice%2C%20smoky%20and%20earthy%20flavor%2C%26quot%3B%20Bhardwaj%20shared.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBe%20mindful%20of%20overcooking%2C%20though%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20only%20trying%20to%20enhance%20flavor%20and%20texture.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-make-the-best-grilled-chicken-tips-from-chef-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echicken%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20still%20get%20cooked%20in%20the%20sauce%20later%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAdd%20your%20chicken%20to%20the%20curry%20in%20the%20last%2020%20minutes%20of%20cooking.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223728%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20adds%20cream%20and%20chicken%20to%20butter%20chicken.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670ff1c43f2165d716e1fce6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222796%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBhardwaj%20recommends%20adding%20the%20oven-grilled%20chicken%20to%20your%20sauce%20in%20the%20last%2020%20minutes%20of%20cooking.%3Cp%3EIndranil%20Mukherjee%2FAFP%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20you%20notice%20a%20light%20char%20and%20the%20skin%20texture%20change%2C%20remove%20it%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-air-fryer-toaster-ovens%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoven%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20mix%20it%20with%20the%20sauce%20after%20a%20few%20seconds%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bhardwaj.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20last%20steps%2C%20let%20the%20chicken%20cook%20in%20the%20sauce%20