P%20Can't%20Afford%20To%20Falter%20In%20Vidarbha%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Ff3v72mkg_vidarbha_625x300_17_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20polling%20dates%20announced%20for%20November%2020%2C%20all%20eyes%20are%20on%20the%20grand%20battle%20in%20Maharashtra.%20The%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20(MVA)%2C%20comprising%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray-led%20Shiv%20Sena%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar-led%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%2C%20is%20anticipating%20a%20victory%20after%20delivering%20a%20shocking%20defeat%20to%20the%20Mahayuti%20coalition%E2%80%94consisting%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20and%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar-led%20NCP%E2%80%94in%20the%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20MVA%20led%20in%20153%20assembly%20segments%2C%20while%20the%20Mahayuti%20was%20ahead%20in%20126%2C%20falling%20short%20of%20the%20simple%20majority%20mark%20of%20145.%20Meanwhile%2C%20buoyed%20by%20its%20recent%20victory%20in%20Haryana%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20confident%20it%20can%20turn%20the%20tide%20through%20its%20cash%20transfer%20scheme%20for%20women%20and%20a%20focus%20on%20infrastructure%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20is%20divided%20into%20six%20regions%3A%20Vidarbha%2C%20North%20Maharashtra%2C%20Western%20Maharashtra%2C%20Marathwada%2C%20Thane-Konkan%2C%20and%20Mumbai.%20Each%20region%20has%20its%20own%20socio-political%20and%20economic%20dynamics.%20Vidarbha%20has%2062%20seats%2C%20North%20Maharashtra%20has%2035%2C%20Marathwada%2046%2C%20Western%20Maharashtra%2070%2C%20Thane-Konkan%2039%2C%20and%20the%20Mumbai%20region%2036%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Kingmaker%20Region%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20Vidarbha%20with%20its%2062%20seats%20that%20could%20be%20the%20kingmaker%20in%20this%20election.%20The%20contest%20here%20is%20predominantly%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP.%20This%20region%20is%20home%20to%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20headquarters%20and%20forms%20the%20eastern%20part%20of%20the%20state%2C%20encompassing%20the%20Amravati%20(formerly%20Berar)%20and%20Nagpur%20divisions.%20According%20to%20the%202011%20census%2C%20Hindus%20make%20up%2077%25%20of%20the%20population%2C%20Muslims%208%25%2C%20and%20Buddhists%2013%25.%20Notably%2C%20Vidarbha%20accounts%20for%2046%25%20of%20the%20total%20Buddhists%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEconomically%2C%20Vidarbha%20is%20underdeveloped%20compared%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20state%2C%20facing%20significant%20poverty%20and%20malnutrition.%20The%20region's%20economy%20is%20heavily%20reliant%20on%20agriculture%2C%20but%20since%202012%2C%20it%20has%20been%20grappling%20with%20severe%20drought%20conditions.%20Tragically%2C%20Vidarbha%20is%20a%20hotspot%20for%20farmer%20suicides%2C%20accounting%20for%2050%25%20of%20such%20cases%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHistorically%2C%20this%20region%20has%20seen%20close%20contests%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress.%20In%201999%2C%20the%20Congress%20won%2024%20seats%20while%20the%20BJP%20secured%2023.%20The%20numbers%20fluctuated%20in%20subsequent%20elections%3A%20in%202004%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%2018%20and%20the%20Congress%2019%3B%20in%202009%2C%20the%20Congress%20took%2024%20and%20the%20BJP%2019.%20In%202014%2C%20riding%20on%20a%20strong%20Lok%20Sabha%20performance%20and%20the%20Modi%20wave%2C%20the%20BJP%20swept%20the%20region%2C%20winning%2044%20seats%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%20was%20reduced%20to%2010.%20This%20marked%20a%20significant%20rise%20for%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%202019%2C%20the%20BJP's%20tally%20fell%20to%2029%20seats%20while%20the%20Congress%20increased%20its%20count%20to%2015.%20This%20decline%20was%20attributed%20to%20agricultural%20distress%2C%20farmer%20suicides%2C%20and%20factionalism%20between%20the%20different%20camps%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20statewide%20drop%20from%20122%20seats%20in%202014%20to%20105%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELearning%20From%20The%20Lok%20Sabha%20Polls%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202024%20general%20elections%2C%20the%20tables%20turned%2C%20with%20the%20Congress%20leading%20in%2029%20seats%20compared%20to%20the%20BJP's%2015.%20The%20MVA%20led%20in%2042%20seats%20against%20the%20Mahayuti's%2019%2C%20giving%20the%20former%20a%20significant%2023-seat%20advantage.%20Of%20the%2010%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20the%20Congress%20won%20five%20and%20the%20BJP%20two%2C%20while%20the%20MVA%20secured%20seven%20and%20the%20Mahayuti%20three.%20In%20terms%20of%20vote%20share%2C%20the%20Congress%20received%2032%25%20votes%2C%20the%20BJP%2030%25%2C%20the%20MVA%2045%25%2C%20and%20the%20Mahayuti%2042%25.%20Notably%2C%20the%20Congress%20won%20five%20of%20the%20seven%20direct%20contest%20seats%20against%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20did%20the%20Congress%20achieve%20this%20success%3F%20The%20party%20capitalised%20on%20agricultural%20distress%20and%20farmer%20discontent%20in%20the%20region.%20Its%20promise%20of%20guaranteeing%20minimum%20support%20prices%20(MSP)%20resonated%20with%20farmers%20suffering%20from%20drought%20and%20suicides.%20Farmers%20in%20Vidarbha%2C%20once%20BJP%20supporters%2C%20became%20disillusioned%20due%20to%20low%20crop%20prices%2C%20high%20input%20costs%2C%20and%20below-MSP%20rates.%20Additional%20issues%20like%20unemployment%20and%20rising%20prices%20compounded%20the%20BJP's%20challenges%20in%20this%20struggling%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20successfully%20formed%20a%20coalition%20with%20various%20social%20groups%2C%20including%20Dalits%2C%20Maratha-Muslim%2C%20and%20Kunbi%20communities%2C%20which%20backed%20the%20party%20and%20MVA%20candidates.%20Dalits%20gravitated%20towards%20the%20Congress%20due%20to%20concerns%20about%20potential%20constitutional%20changes%20and%20the%20end%20of%20reservations%20if%20the%20BJP%20crossed%20400%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnti-incumbency%20sentiment%20also%20played%20a%20role%2C%20with%20established%20politicians%20facing%20backlash%20over%20non-performance%2C%20resulting%20in%20defeats%20by%20newcomers%20from%20the%20MVA.%20Additionally%2C%20urban%20strongholds%20of%20the%20BJP%20saw%20lower%20turnout%2C%20with%20even%20Nitin%20Gadkari%20experiencing%20a%20reduced%20victory%20margin%20compared%20to%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Kingmaker%20Region%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVidarbha%20represents%2062%20out%20of%20288%20assembly%20seats%2C%20constituting%2022%25%20of%20the%20house's%20strength.%20Notably%2C%20BJP%20leaders%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20and%20Nitin%20Gadkari%20hail%20from%20Vidarbha%2C%20as%20do%20MPCC%20Chief%20Nana%20Patole%20and%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20Vijay%20Wadettiwar.%20The%20NCP%20and%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20have%20limited%20influence%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20this%20region%20is%20also%20characterised%20by%20significant%20rural%20and%20agricultural%20distress%2C%20there%20could%20be%20heightened%20anti-incumbency%20against%20the%20Mahayuti%20coalition.%20Demographically%2C%20some%20social%20groups%20lean%20towards%20the%20Congress%2C%20making%20it%20essential%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20address%20farmers'%20grievances%20effectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20optimistic%20that%20initiatives%20like%20the%20Ladki%20Bahin%2C%20a%20cash%20transfer%20programme%20for%20women%2C%20granting%20constitutional%20status%20to%20the%20SC%20Commission%2C%20and%20raising%20the%20OBC%20creamy%20layer%20cap%20will%20help%20mitigate%20discontent%20in%20the%20region.%20Historically%2C%20the%20winner%20of%20Vidarbha%20has%20gone%20on%20to%20secure%20the%20state%20elections%2C%20a%20trend%20evident%20over%20the%20past%20five%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHome%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20stressed%20the%20importance%20of%20winning%20Vidarbha%20to%20maintain%20power%2C%20and%20the%20BJP%20must%20reverse%20the%20trend%20observed%20in%20this%20year's%20general%20elections.%20The%20recent%20victory%20in%20Haryana%20may%20bolster%20their%20confidence%20to%20achieve%20what%20seemed%20challenging%20just%20weeks%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729172640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F7otohe1o_vidarbha_625x300_17_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmaharashtra-why-bjp-cant-afford-to-lose-vidarbha-again-6811754%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Historically%2C%20this%20region%20has%20seen%20close%20contests%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmaharashtra-why-bjp-cant-afford-to-lose-vidarbha-again-6811754%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hamas%20Chief%20Yahya%20Sinwar%20Killed%20In%20Gaza%20Strike%3F%20%26quot%3BChecking%26quot%3B%2C%20Says%20Israel%20Army%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20said%20on%20Thursday%20that%20it%20was%20checking%20the%20possibility%20that%20it%20has%20killed%20Hamas%20leader%20Yahya%20Sinwar%20following%20an%20operation%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20that%20it%20said%20had%20targeted%20three%20militants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20this%20stage%2C%20the%20identity%20of%2