t%20I%20had%20the%20energy%20and%20willpower%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20a%20little%20kid.%20Besides%2C%20it%20seemed%20the%20right%20thing%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20son%20and%20daughter-in-law%20worked%20long%20hours%20in%20demanding%20jobs.%20I%20know%20that%20if%20I%20hadn't%20agreed%20to%20watch%20their%20daughter%2C%20they'd%20have%20managed%20somehow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20stress%20would%20have%20been%20amplified%20if%20they%20didn't%20have%20a%20family%20to%20help%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a0eb79c3-999b-4057-9bc9-a33048dceb3f%5C%22%3EI%20received%20%24300%20for%2030%20hours%20of%20childcare%20the%20first%20week%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20initial%20plan%20was%20for%20me%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrandparents-moved-from-india-to-us-provide-free-childcare-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprovide%20childcare%3C%2Fa%3E%20four%20days%20a%20week%2C%20sometimes%20with%20my%20husband%2C%20while%20my%20daughter-in-law's%20parents%20covered%20the%20other%20day%20and%20sometimes%20a%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20very%20enthusiastic%20because%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20had%20to%20offer%20my%20grandchildren.%20I'd%20previously%20gotten%20a%20day%20care%20license%20after%20taking%20classes%20at%20a%20community%20college.%20I'd%20been%20thinking%20about%20running%20my%20own%20business%20from%20home.%20I%20decided%20against%20it%2C%20mostly%20because%20of%20the%20high%20insurance%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20my%20son%20and%20daughter-in-law's%20accountant%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMaybe%20you%20could%20pay%20your%20family%20for%20childcare%20and%20apply%20it%20to%20your%20taxes%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20when%20I%20formally%20watched%20my%20granddaughter%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20they%20paid%20me%20around%20%24300.%20It%20worked%20out%20at%20about%20%2410%20an%20hour%20%E2%80%94%20the%20same%20rate%20I'd%20earned%20in%20retail.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20as%20soon%20as%20they%20gave%20me%20the%20salary%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20week%2C%20I%20felt%20so%20guilty%20%E2%80%94%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funexpected-signs-you-are-a-star-employee-2016-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eas%20if%20I%20was%20an%20employee%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BThis%20can't%20happen%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20told%20my%20son.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20a%20grandma%2C%20not%20a%20granny-nanny.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d7487c81-df6b-49f2-9bbd-8c5b2b3faeb6%5C%22%3EI%20now%20provide%20childcare%20for%20free%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wasn't%20in%20it%20for%20the%20money.%20Compensation%20can't%20pay%20for%20the%20memories%20of%20being%20with%20my%20grandchildren.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wanted%20them%20to%20take%20back%20the%20dollars%2C%20but%20they%20said%20to%20keep%20them%20that%20once%20to%20put%20toward%20things%20I'd%20already%20bought%2C%20like%20cribs%2C%20dressers%2C%20and%20bouncy%20toys.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%2C%20I%20did%20everything%20for%20free.%20My%20husband%20picked%20up%20some%20extra%20hours%20at%20work%2C%20which%20went%20toward%20the%20income%20I%20no%20longer%20brought%20in.%20Still%2C%20people%20would%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20know%2C%20you're%20affecting%20yourself%20financially.%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20told%20them%20I%20was%20giving%20a%20gift%20to%20my%20son%2C%20daughter-in-law%20and%20grandchildren%20that%20was%20priceless.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20watched%20my%20granddaughter%2C%20now%2010%2C%20at%20my%20home%20from%20around%206%3A30%20a.m.%20to%205%20p.m.%20Her%20parents%20would%20drop%20her%20off%20and%20pick%20her%20up.%20They%20did%20the%20same%20when%20her%20little%20brother%2C%20now%208%2C%20was%20born.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20they%20had%20to%20work%20late%2C%20I'd%20drive%20the%20kids%20to%20their%20home%20and%20stay%20as%20long%20as%20was%20needed%20%E2%80%94%20sometimes%2010%20p.m.%20We%20were%20fortunate%20they%20only%20lived%20four%20miles%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C