%2Fcat-got-cancer-assessed-pet-insurance-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20current%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAffiliate%20links%20for%20the%20products%20on%20this%20page%20are%20from%20partners%20that%20compensate%20us%20(see%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Four-partners%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadvertiser%20disclosure%20with%20our%20list%20of%20partners%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more%20details).%20However%2C%20our%20opinions%20are%20our%20own.%20See%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fpet-insurance%2Fmethodology%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20we%20rate%20pet%20insurance%20products%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20write%20unbiased%20product%20reviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chris%20Boutt%C3%A9%20holds%20his%20cat%20in%20his%20arms.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670ee35d6ac7b701e7cbe89d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221516%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%2C%20Chris%20Boutt%C3%A9%2C%20and%20his%20cat.%3Cp%3EChris%20Boutt%C3%A9%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMy%20girlfriend%20and%20I%20never%20talked%20about%20pet%20insurance%20%E2%80%94%20that%20changed%20when%20our%20cat%20got%20cancer.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWe%20spent%20over%20%243%2C500%20trying%20to%20save%20him%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20I%20would%20spend%20that%20much%20again.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EI%20haven't%20decided%20whether%20pet%20insurance%20is%20right%20for%20my%20needs%2C%20but%20I%20know%20I'm%20willing%20to%20take%20on%20debt%20for%20my%20pets.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%20was%20one%20of%20the%20most%20difficult%20years%20of%20my%20life%2C%20and%20I've%20been%20through%20a%20lot%20in%20my%20time%20on%20this%20planet.%20In%20the%20summer%20of%202023%2C%20my%20girlfriend's%20cat%2C%20Wyatt%2C%20started%20to%20get%20really%20sick.%20I%20never%20owned%20pets%20before%20meeting%20Wyatt%2C%20so%20I%20didn't%20know%20I%20could%20love%20an%20animal%20that%20much.%20However%2C%20after%20seven%20years%20of%20knowing%20him%2C%20when%20we%20found%20out%20he%20had%20cancer%20and%20wasn't%20going%20to%20make%20it%2C%20it%20destroyed%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20this%20difficult%20time%2C%20we%20had%20enough%20occupying%20our%20thoughts%20and%20emotions%2C%20and%20the%20last%20thing%20we%20wanted%20to%20worry%20about%20was%20the%20cost.%20But%20without%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fpet-insurance%2Fbest-pet-insurance%5C%22%3Epet%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20had%20to%20make%20tough%20decisions%20as%20we%20tried%20to%20save%20his%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWe%20didn't%20think%20about%20pet%20insurance%20until%20we%20needed%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20adopted%20my%20cat%2C%20Maya%2C%20around%20the%20time%20my%20girlfriend%20and%20I%20started%20dating%2C%20and%20we%20moved%20in%20together%20about%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20into%20our%20relationship.%20We%20never%20really%20talked%20about%20pet%20insurance%20because%20our%20cats%20never%20really%20got%20sick.%20That's%20what's%20tricky%20about%20insurance%3B%20by%20the%20time%20you%20need%20it%2C%20it's%20too%20late.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWyatt%20was%20always%20pretty%20chunky%2C%20and%20in%202022%2C%20we%20found%20out%20he%20had%20diabetes%20after%20noticing%20he%20was%20limping%20a%20little.%20The%20tests%20to%20diagnose%20him%20cost%20us%20hundreds%2C%20and%20then%20they%20wanted%20him%20to%20come%20back%20weekly%20to%20check%20his%20blood%20sugar.%20This%20would%20have%20cost%20%2440%20a%20week%2C%20so%20we%20bought%20an%20iPet%20PRO%20for%20blood%20glucose%20monitoring%20and%20tested%20him%20regularly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20girlfriend%20wasn't%20a%20fan%20of%20having%20to%20poke%20Wyatt%20to%20check%20his%20blood%20and%20give%20him%20daily%20insulin%20injections%2C%20so%20I%20took%20on%20that%20task.%20I%20gave%20him%20his%20injections%20daily%20and%20checked%20his%20glucose%20throughout%20the%20week.%20Doing%20it%20at%20home%20saved%20us%20quite%20a%20bit%20of%20money%2C%20and%20we%20used%20an%20app%20to%20track%20his%20progress.%20Luckily%2C%20we%20had%20an%20awesome%20vet%20who%20let%20us%20email%20the%20results%2C%20and%20she'd%20let%20us%20know%20if%20we%20needed%20to%20adjust%20his%20dose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWyatt's%20health%20took%20a%20turn%20for%20the%20worse%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20almost%20a%20year%20later%2C%20his%20blood%20sugar%20was%20under%20control%2C%20and%20he%20barely%20needed%20any%20insulin.%20Then%2C%20out%20of%20nowhere%2C%20he%20took%20a%20turn%20for%20the%20worse.%20We%20noticed%20he%20was%20hiding%20and%20super%20lethargic%20and%20decided%20to%20bring%20him%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20work-from-home%20schedule%20gives%20me%20a%20lot%20of%20flexibility%2C%20so%20I%20took%20him%20to%20all%20of%20his%20vet%20appointments%2C%20and%20it%20was%20rough.%20On%20the%20first%20visit%2C%20we%20were%20there%20for%20hours%20as%20they%20did%20various%20tests.%20At%20first%2C%20they%20thought%20it%20was%20just%20a%20normal%20sickness%2C%20but%20when%20he%20didn't%20get%20better%2C%20we%20had%20to%20bring%20him%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20proceeded%20to%20give%20him%20X-rays%20to%20check%20for%20cancer%2C%20but%20it%20was%20difficult%20to%20tell%20for%20sure.%20By%20this%20time%2C%20we%20had%20spent%20a%20little%20over%20%241%2C000%20on%20all%20of%20the%20tests.%20The%20vet%20was%20optimistic%20it%20wasn't%20cancer%20because%20he'd%20start%20feeling%20better%2C%20but%20then%20he'd%20get%20worse%20out%20of%20nowhere.%20Our%20vet%20said%20we%20could%20do%20a%20biopsy%20to%20be%20certain%2C%20and%20it%20was%20about%20%241%2C200%2C%20so%20she%20said%20we%20didn't%20really%20need%20to%20unless%20it%20seemed%20like%20he%20got%20really%20bad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20day%2C%20that's%20exactly%20what%20happened%2C%20and%20I%20rushed%20him%20to%20an%20ER.%20They%20said%20they%20thought%20it%20might%20be%20cancer%2C%20so%20we%20decided%20to%20get%20the%20biopsy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWyatt%20was%20suffering%20a%20lot%2C%20and%20if%20we%20had%20to%20put%20him%20to%20sleep%2C%20we%20just%20wanted%20to%20know%20sooner%20rather%20than%20later%2C%20so%20we%20paid%20a%20couple%20extra%20hundred%20dollars%20to%20rush%20the%20results.%20After%20a%20few%20days%2C%20we%20sadly%20found%20out%20he%20had%20a%20form%20of%20cancer%20that%20wasn't%20really%20treatable%2C%20even%20if%20we%20had%20caught%20it%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20the%20week%2C%20we%20had%20to%20say%20goodbye%20to%20Wyatt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWe%20haven't%20gotten%20pet%20insurance%20yet%2C%20but%20we're%20taking%20steps%20to%20be%20prepared%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20before%20we%20got%20Wyatt%2C%20we%20adopted%20our%20cat%2C%20Dolly%2C%20an%20adorable%20flat-faced%20exotic%20short%20hair.%20Wyatt%20was%20extremely%20cuddly%2C%20and%20girl%20cats%20don't%20cuddle%20as%20much%2C%20so%20once%20my%20girlfriend%20was%20ready%2C%20we%20adopted%20our%20third%20cat%2C%20Chester.%20Now%2C%20we%20have%20three%20cats%20we%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20getting%20sick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20that%20whole%20scenario%20with%20Wyatt%2C%20I%20kept%20asking%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20much%20money%20should%20you%20spend%20to%20save%20your%20animal's%20life%3F%26quot%3B%20It's%20a%20difficult%20philosophical%20question%2C%20and%20we%20ended%20up%20spending%20over%20%243%2C500%20trying%20to%20save%20Wyatt.%20After%20years%20of%20trying%20to%20fix%20my%20financial%20situation%2C%20I%20have%20to%20ask%20myself%20%E2%80%94%20am%20I%20willing%20to%20do%20that%20with%20each%20of%20our%20cats%2C%20or%20should%20we%20get%20pet%20insurance%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20should%20probably%20get%20pet%20insurance%2C%20but%20we%20haven't%20yet.%20The%20primary%20reason%20is%20that%20pet%20insurance%20is%20worse%20than%20pre-Obamacare%20human%20insurance%2C%20and%20it%20doesn't%2