(%40flightradar24)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fflightradar24%2Fstatus%2F1846875391752855901%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2017%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AI129%20flight%20declared%20an%20emergency%20an%20hour%20before%20landing.%20It%20was%20scheduled%20to%20land%20at%20Heathrow%20Airport%20in%20London%20at%2012%3A05%20pm%20(UK%20time).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20latest%20information%20from%20FlightRadar24%2C%20the%20aircraft%20is%20no%20longer%20'squawking%207700'%20and%20landed%20at%20Heathrow%20Airport.%20'Squawking%207700'%20notifies%20the%20nearby%20Air%20Traffic%20Controllers%20of%20the%20situation%20onboard%20the%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F5-year-flight-ban-for-hoax-callers-say-sources-amid-bomb-threat-to-airlines-6803649%5C%22%3EThe%20pattern%20of%20airlines%20receiving%20bomb%20threats%3C%2Fa%3E%20continued%20for%20the%20fourth%20consecutive%20day%2C%20with%20at%20least%2020%20aircraft%20getting%20threats%20in%20four%20days.%20Today%2C%20five%20Air%20India%20flights%2C%20two%20Vistara%20and%20two%20IndiGo%20flights%20received%20bomb%20threats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmumbai-news%2F2-mumbai-bound-international-flights-receive-bomb-threats-forced-to-land-6809729%5C%22%3EA%20Mumbai-bound%20Vistara%20flight%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20147%20persons%20on%20board%20was%20immediately%20taken%20to%20security%20checks%20on%20its%20arrival%20from%20Frankfurt%20following%20the%20Boeing%20787%20aircraft%20receiving%20a%20bomb%20threat%2C%20according%20to%20the%20airline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVistara%20flight%20UK%20028%20operating%20from%20Frankfurt%20to%20Mumbai%20on%2016%20October%202024%20was%20subject%20to%20a%20security%20threat%20received%20on%20social%20media.%20As%20per%20protocol%2C%20all%20relevant%20authorities%20were%20immediately%20informed.%20The%20aircraft%20safely%20landed%20at%20the%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%20International%20Airport%2C%20Mumbai%20and%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20isolation%20bay%20where%20all%20customers%20were%20disembarked.%20We%20are%20fully%20cooperating%20with%20the%20security%20agencies%20to%20complete%20the%20mandatory%20security%20checks.%20At%20Vistara%2C%20the%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20our%20customers%2C%20crew%20and%20aircraft%20are%20of%20utmost%20importance%20to%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Vistara%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20an%20IndiGo%20flight%20operating%20from%20Istanbul%20to%20Turkiye%20for%20Mumbai%20also%20received%20a%20bomb%20threat%20and%20was%20taken%20to%20an%20isolation%20bay%20here%20for%20the%20security%20agencies%20to%20carry%20out%20a%20comprehensive%20security%20check.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndiGo%20in%20a%20statement%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFlight%206E%2018%2C%20operating%20from%20Istanbul%20to%20Mumbai%2C%20received%20a%20security-related%20alert.%20Upon%20landing%2C%20the%20aircraft%20was%20isolated%2C%20and%20all%20passengers%20were%20safely%20disembarked.%26quot%3B%20The%20airline%20worked%20closely%20with%20the%20relevant%20authorities%2C%20and%20standard%20operating%20procedures%20were%20followed%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndiGo%2C%20however%2C%20did%20not%20share%20other%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAction%20Plan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20told%20NDTV%20earlier%20that%20the%20Centre%20and%20civil%20authorities%20are%20working%20together%20to%20handle%20the%20crisis.%20The%20Home%20Ministry%20asked%20the%20Civil%20Aviation%20Ministry%20to%20send%20a%20detailed%20report%20on%20the%20incidents.%20Airlines%20have%20been%20asked%20by%20the%20aviation%20ministry%20to%20provide%20inputs%20on%20the%20bomb%20scare%20incidents%2C%20based%20on%20which%2C%20the%20Directorate%20General%20of%20Civil%20Aviation%20(DGCA)%20will%20prepare%20a%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Parliamentary%20Standing%20Committee%20met%20over%20the%20issue%20yesterday.%20This%20was%20preceded%20by%20a%20meeting%20called%20by%20Civil%20Aviation%20Minister%20Ram%20Mohan%20Naidu%20with%20the%20Civil%20Aviation%20Ministry%20and%20DGCA%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fclosely-monitoring-situation-of-bomb-threats-to-airlines-says-aviation-minister-6805334%5C%22%3EWe%20are%20closely%20monitoring%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20situation%20and%20ensuring%20that%20We%20are%20committed%20to%20maintaining%20the%20highest%20security%20standards%20and%20passenger%20safety%20remains%20our%20topmost%20priority%2C%26quot%3B%20Civil%20Aviation%20Minister%20K%20Rammohan%20Naidu%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20several%20steps%20will%20be%20taken%20to%20deal%20with%20such%20situations%3A%20Those%20who%20post%20bomb%20threats%20will%20be%20added%20to%20the%20'Unruly%20Passengers'%20list.%20The%20airlines%20have%20suggested%20that%20they%20should%20be%20banned%20from%20flying%20for%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20that%20airlines%20suggested%20that%20losses%20borne%20by%20them%20due%20to%20fake%20bomb%20threats%20should%20be%20recovered%20from%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20names%20of%20those%20responsible%20for%20hoax%20calls%20will%20be%20shared%20with%20the%20airline%20and%20security%20agencies.%20The%20Civil%20Aviation%20Ministry%20is%20expected%20to%20share%20the%20guidelines%20soon.%20The%20ministry%20will%20also%20share%20a%20detailed%20report%20on%20the%20bomb%20scare%20investigation%20in%20two%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20has%20ordered%20the%20Central%20Industrial%20Security%20Force%20(CISF)%20to%20stay%20alert%20at%20the%20airports.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729168920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-01%2Ff1pka8d8_air-india-boeing-777_625x300_27_January_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2F