20fall%20of%206th%20wicket%20for%20India%20at%20home%20since%201969.%20The%20previous%20lowest%20was%2027%20runs%20against%20New%20Zealand%20at%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20also%20the%20first%20time%20in%20world%20cricket%20since%201888%20that%20five%20out%20of%20a%20team's%20top%20eight%20batters%20were%20dismissed%20for%20a%C2%A0%20duck.%20The%20first%20time-ever%20it%20happened%20was%20in%201888%20when%20Australia%20collapsed%20in%20a%20Test%20match%20against%20England.%20India%20are%20the%20first%20Asian%20team%20to%20achieve%20the%20feat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20folded%20for%20an%20embarrassing%C2%A046%C2%A0in%20only%2031.2%20overs%20to%20record%20their%20lowest-ever%20total%20in%20293%20home%20Test%20matches%20on%20Thursday%2C%20undone%20by%20New%20Zealand%20pace%20attack's%20brilliant%20use%20of%20the%20overcast%20conditions.%20This%C2%A046%C2%A0all-out%2C%20which%20included%20five%20batters%20getting%20dismissed%20for%20ducks%2C%20was%20the%20first%20instance%20in%20which%20the%20team%20failed%20to%20cross%20the%2050-run%20mark%20in%20a%20Test%20innings%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20the%20second%20time%20that%20five%20Indian%20batters%20failing%20to%20open%20their%20accounts%20against%20the%20Kiwis%20in%20a%20Test%20at%20home%2C%20after%20the%20Mohali%20Test%20in%201999.%20The%20previous%20Indian%20record%20of%20lowest%20Test%20innings%20total%20at%20home%20came%20nearly%2037%20years%20ago%2C%20against%20the%20West%20Indies%20in%20November%2C%201987%20at%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20overall%20lowest%2C%20however%2C%20was%20recorded%20four%20years%20ago%20against%20Australia%20when%20they%20were%20shot%20out%20for%20a%20mere%2036%20at%20Adelaide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20is%20a%20list%20of%20India's%20lowest%20ever%20totals%20in%20the%20traditional%20format%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHome%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E46%C2%A0in%2031.2%20overs%20vs%20New%20Ze