desh%20Prime%20Minister%20Sheikh%20Hasina%2C%20who%20came%20to%20India%20in%20early%20August%2C%20is%20still%20in%20the%20country%2C%20the%20foreign%20ministry%20said%20today%20after%20a%20court%20in%20Bangladesh%20ordered%20her%20arrest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20stay%20of%20the%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20I%20had%20earlier%20mentioned%20that%20she%20had%20come%20here%20at%20a%20short%20notice%20and%20she%20continues%20to%20be%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheikh%20Hasina%20had%20arrived%20in%20India%20on%20August%205%2C%20as%20an%20uprising%20led%20by%20students%20against%20her%20turned%20violent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20had%20not%20mentioned%20how%20long%20she%20would%20stay%20and%20there%20was%20much%20speculation%20about%20her%20final%20destination.%20A%20number%20of%20names%20have%20come%20up%2C%20including%20US%2C%20UK%20and%20even%20Finland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20very%20short%20notice%2C%20she%20requested%20approval%20to%20come%20for%20the%20moment%20to%20India.%20We%20simultaneously%20received%20a%20request%20for%20flight%20clearance%20from%20the%20Bangladesh%20authorities.%20She%20arrived%20yesterday%20evening%20in%20Delhi%2C%26quot%3B%20foreign%20minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%20a%20day%20after%20she%20landed%20at%C2%A0%20the%20Hindon%20airport%2C%20near%20Delhi.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20son%20Sajeeb%20Wazed%2C%20who%20is%20based%20in%20Washington%2C%20had%20said%20the%2076-year-old%20was%20contemplating%20retirement%20and%20is%20likely%20to%20divide%20her%20time%20between%20her%20family%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20multiple%20reports%20about%20UK's%20%26quot%3Bsilence%26quot%3B%20her%20request%20for%20asylum%20and%20revocation%20of%20her%20visa%20by%20the%20US%2C%20he%20had%20said%20that%20she%20has%20not%20requested%20asylum%20%26quot%3Banywhere%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Bangladesh's%20International%20Crimes%20Tribu