ance%20with%20claim%20triage%20and%20handling%2C%20and%20we%20embed%20insurance%20into%20the%20apps%20so%20that%20it's%20accessible%20for%20drivers%2C%26quot%3B%20Inshur's%20CEO%2C%20Dan%20Bratshpis%2C%20told%20BI.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20products%20are%20used%20by%20ride-hailing%20clients%20such%20as%20Uber%20and%20can%20be%20embedded%20into%20a%20company's%20existing%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Uber%20drivers%20can%20log%20in%20using%20their%20Uber%20credentials%20on%20the%20Inshur%20app%2C%20to%20get%20a%20quote%2C%20said%20Bratshpis.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20we're%20embedded%2C%20we%20can%20pull%20data%20from%20Uber%20and%20underwrite%20a%20fair%20and%20comprehensive%20policy%20for%20the%20on-demand%20driver%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20claims%20that%20its%20car-sharing%20insurance%20platform%20has%20grown%20by%20100%25%20in%20the%20past%20year.%20In%20April%2C%20it%20acquired%20American%20Business%20Insurance%20Services%20and%20has%20since%20expanded%20its%20footprint%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Series%20B%2C%20led%20by%20Viola%20Growth%20and%20with%20participation%20from%20MS%26amp%3BAD%2C%20brings%20the%20startup's%20total%20funding%20to%20%2480%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20capital%20injection%2C%20Inshur%20said%20it%20will%20continue%20to%20scale%20its%20team%20in%20the%20US%2C%20and%20develop%20its%20product%20offerings%20for%20drivers%20and%20commercial%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECheck%20out%20the%2016-slide%20pitch%20deck%20used%20to%20secure%20the%20fresh%20funding.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Inshur%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6710d43e6ac7b701e7ccbe45%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22844%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EInshur%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22I