20Ajay%20Kashyap%20alias%20AK%20and%20four%20others%20involved%20in%20the%20conspiracy.%20A%20recce%20by%20Kashyap%20and%20his%20team%20led%20to%20the%20conclusion%20that%20owing%20to%20the%20actor's%20tight%20security%20and%20bulletproof%20vehicles%2C%20high-end%20weapons%20would%20be%20required%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESukkha%20contacted%20Pakistan-based%20arms%20dealer%20Dogar%20through%20video%20call%2C%C2%A0showing%20AK-47%20and%20other%20advanced%20fire%20arms%20wrapped%20in%20a%20shawl%2C%20while%20negotiating%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20arms%20deal.%C2%A0Dogar%20agreed%20to%20supply%20the%20weapons%2C%20while%20Sukha%20agreed%20to%20make%2050%20percent%20advance%20payment%20and%20the%20remaining%20amount%20on%20delivery%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%C2%A0also%20found%20that%20all%20the%20shooters%20were%20waiting%20for%C2%A0a%20go-ahead%20from%20Canada-based%20gangster%20Goldie%20Brar%20and%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi's%20brother%20Anmol%20Bishnoi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chargesheet%20also%20details%20a%20plan%20made%20by%20the%20shooters%20to%20gather%20in%20Kanyakumari%20after%20shooting%20the%2058-year-old%20actor%2C%20from%20where%20they%20would%20travel%20to%20Sri%20Lanka%20by%20boat%20and%20then%20to%20a%20country%20where%20Indian%20investigation%20agencies%20could%20not%20reach%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conspiracy%20to%20target%20Salman%20Khan%20at%20his%20Panvel%20farmhouse%20was%20unearthed%20when%20the%20police%20was%20investigation%20the%20incident%20of%20firing%20outside%20his%20house%20in%20Bandra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsecurity-increased-at-salman-khans-bandra-home-after-baba-siddique-murder-6785159%5C%22%3Esecurity%20has%20been%20increased%3C%2Fa%3E%20outside%C2%A0Salman%20Khan's%20Bandra%20residence%20following%20the%20killing%20of%20former%20minister%20and%20NCP%20leader%20Baba%20Siddique.%20The%20latter%2C%20a%20former%20ML