ing%20until%20they%20reached%201%2C50%2C000%20followers%20and%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20in%20organic%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20D2C%20business%2C%20trust-building%20is%20most%20important%20and%20can%20happen%20only%20through%20organic%20sales%20in%20the%20beginning.%20My%20goal%20was%20to%20create%20a%20difference%20in%20people%E2%80%99s%20lives%2C%20which%20I%20was%20able%20to%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20Haripriya%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20they%20have%20nearly%205%2C00%2C000%20followers%20on%20Instagram%20and%20receive%20over%2015%2C000%20orders%20a%20month.%20Their%20toys%20start%20from%20Rs%2049%20to%20Rs%208%2C000%20and%20include%20educational%20toys%2C%20family%20games%2C%20open-ended%20toys%2C%20pretend%20play%20items%2C%20magnatiles%2C%20kinetic%20sand%2C%20and%20much%20more.%20Their%20bestsellers%20include%20puzzles%2C%20memory%20card%20games%2C%20and%20%E2%80%9CShut%20the%20Box.%E2%80%9D%20Haripriya%20adds%20that%20most%20of%20the%20toys%20are%20open%20ended%2C%20meaning%20children%20of%20various%20age%20groups%20can%20play%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Have%20a%20vision%20and%20take%20calculated%20risks%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20moment%20for%20Haripriya%20was%20when%20one%20of%20their%20videos%20went%20viral%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20surge%20in%20orders.%20They%20had%20to%20work%20until%202%20AM%20to%20dispatch%20the%20orders%2C%20as%20they%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20hold%20them%20for%20more%20than%20two%20days.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20ups%20and%20downs%2C%20losses%20and%20profits%2C%20her%20mother%2C%2052-year-old%20Banu%2C%20has%20been%20her%20constant%20support.%20Today%2C%20Banu%20is%20a%20familiar%20face%20%E2%80%94%20the%20enthusiastic%20woman%20who%20explains%20the%20workings%20of%20toys%20online.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaised%20in%20Coimbatore%20in%20a%20business%20family%2C%20Banu%20spent%20most%20of%20her%20life%20as%20a%20homemaker.%20While%20she%2