cy%20and%20homelessness%20in%20the%20US%2C%20Ranveer%20Brar%20returned%20to%20India%2C%20rising%20to%20fame%20as%20a%20renowned%20chef%20and%20TV%20personality.%20From%20cooking%20in%20Lucknow%E2%80%99s%20streets%20to%20judging%20on%20MasterChef%20India%20and%20acting%20alongside%20Kareena%20Kapoor%20in%20The%20Buckingham%20Murders%2C%20his%20journey%20is%20one%20of%20remarkable%20transformation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Khushi%20Arora%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F370403%2Franveer-brar-journey-the-buckingham-murders-kareena-kapoor-watch-video-celebrity-chef-lucknow-masterchef-india%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20This%20Techie%20Gave%20Up%20a%20High-Paying%20Job%20to%20Transform%20Education%20for%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20Tribal%20Children%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20been%20learning%20Python%20%5Ba%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F303942%2Famazon-future-engineer-programme-helps-teachers-students-learn-coding-computer-science-pune%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esoftware%20programming%3C%2Fa%3E%20language%5D.%20I%20even%20designed%20a%20game%20by%20myself%20last%20month!%E2%80%9D%20Roshan%20(13)%20is%20enthusiastic%20about%20divulging%20details%20about%20his%20brainchild%2C%20%E2%80%98Target%E2%80%99.%20%E2%80%9CFirst%2C%20the%20computer%20will%20give%20a%20number.%20If%20you%20can%20guess%20the%20number%20correctly%2C%20you%20win!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20achievement%20goes%20well%20beyond%20a%20mere%20hat%20trick%20for%20Roshan%E2%80%99s%20parents%20and%20teachers.%20It%20is%20a%20metaphor%20for%20his%20diligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20years%20ago%2C%20this%20eighth%20grader%20found%20it%20mind-boggling%20to%20string%20together%20simple%20sentences%20in%20English.%20He%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20ever%20seen%20a%20computer%2C%20let%20alone%20known%20ho