%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20time%20to%20think%20about%20our%20health.%20Even%20when%20we%20rest%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20still%20working.%20I%20also%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to%20rest.%20Rest%2C%20to%20me%2C%20meant%20anxiety%20because%20I%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20doing%20anything%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Slow%20down%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERama%20was%20bogged%20down%20by%20a%20constant%20fear%20of%20the%20future%2C%20which%20didn%E2%80%99t%20allow%20her%20to%20sleep.%20%E2%80%9CI%20feared%20failure%20and%20not%20being%20able%20to%20achieve%20my%20goals.%20I%20had%20cold%20feet%20and%20palpitations.%20Fear%20had%20invaded%20my%20body.%20It%20was%20a%20very%20difficult%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20psychiatrist%20gave%20her%20some%20pills%20to%20begin%20her%20treatment.%20Rama%20also%20called%20her%20mother%20to%20Bengaluru%20for%20support%20while%20her%20husband%20was%20at%20work.%20She%20stayed%20with%20her%20for%20two%20and%20a%20half%20months%2C%20providing%20unwavering%20support%20every%20time%20Rama%20broke%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20her%20mother%20didn%E2%80%99t%20fully%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F315631%2Fbengaluru-punita-mittal-mahak-maheshwari-soulup-mental-health-online-support-platform%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunderstand%20anxiety%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20listened.%20They%20would%20go%20on%20long%20walks%2C%20sometimes%20lasting%20over%20two%20hours%2C%20which%20helped%20Rama%20get%20fresh%20air%2C%20sunlight%2C%20and%20a%20much-needed%20distraction%20from%20her%20thoughts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERama%20notes%20that%20while%20loved%20ones%20may%20not%20fully%20understand%20mental%20health%20issues%2C%20they%20can%20still%20help.%20Over%20time%2C%20her%20husband%20became%20more%20receptive%20to%20her%20needs%20and%20worked%20alongside%20her%20to%20help%20her%20feel