%20discover%20the%20dark%20truth%20behind%20his%20charming%20facade.%20What%20began%20as%20a%20happy%20union%20turned%20into%20a%20nightmare%2C%20as%20she%20found%20herself%20trapped%20in%20a%20cycle%20of%20abuse%20and%20neglect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20six%20months%20of%20marriage%20seemed%20promising%20until%20she%20uncovered%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20alcohol%20addiction.%20Despite%20reaching%20out%20to%20her%20parents%20for%20support%2C%20Ambika%20was%20met%20with%20indifference%20and%20told%20to%20endure%20her%20chosen%20life%20partner%E2%80%99s%20destructive%20behaviour.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20would%20not%20only%20beat%20me%20but%20also%20force%20himself%20on%20me%20daily%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20years%20went%20by%2C%20the%20abuse%20escalated%2C%20and%20Ambika%20found%20herself%20struggling%20to%20make%20ends%20meet%20for%20their%20two%20daughters.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20stopped%20paying%20rent%20for%20our%20home%20and%20would%20not%20even%20give%20me%20money%20to%20buy%20milk%20for%20our%20six-month-old%20child%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20husband%E2%80%99s%20refusal%20to%20provide%20financial%20support%20left%20her%20burdened%20with%20the%20sole%20responsibility%20of%20sustaining%20their%20household.%20She%20started%20balancing%20a%20demanding%20job%20at%20a%20book-binding%20company%20and%20caring%20for%20her%20two%20daughters.%20While%20she%20was%20pushed%20to%20her%20limits%20both%20physically%20and%20mentally%2C%20the%20violence%20at%20home%20didn%E2%80%99t%20stop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20continued%20for%20eight%20years%20until%20one%20day%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20asked%20him%20to%20pay%20at%20least%20for%20the%20groceries%2C%20but%20he%20started%20beating%20me.%20I%20cried%20myself%20to%20sleep%20but%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20woke%20up%20the%20next%20day%2C%20he%20again%20started%20beating%20me.%20I%20was%20exhausted%20of%20this%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ambika%2C%20adding%20that%20that%20was%20when%20she